<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Premium Job Seeker Subscription Activated</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f6fa;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .subscription-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;
        }
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .feature-item {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <!-- Replace with your logo -->
            </div>
            <h1>Welcome to Premium Job Seeker!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{userName}},</p>
            
            <p>Congratulations! ðŸŽ‰ Your premium job seeker subscription has been successfully activated. Get ready to unlock your career potential with our enhanced features!</p>
            
            <div class="subscription-details">
                <h3>Your Subscription Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Plan Type:</strong> {{subscriptionPlan}}</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> {{subscriptionStatus}}</p>
                <p><strong>Activated On:</strong> {{activationDate}}</p>
            </div>
            
            <h3>Your Premium Benefits Include:</h3>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h4>Priority Job Applications</h4>
                    <p>Your profile gets shown first to employers</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h4>Advanced Job Alerts</h4>
                    <p>Get instant notifications for matching jobs</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h4>Profile Highlights</h4>
                    <p>Stand out with a highlighted profile</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-item">
                    <h4>Direct Recruiter Contact</h4>
                    <p>Connect directly with hiring managers</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <center>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Access Your Premium Dashboard</a>
            </center>

            <p>To make the most of your premium subscription:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Update your profile with latest skills and experiences</li>
                <li>Set up job alerts for your preferred positions</li>
                <li>Upload your latest resume</li>
                <li>Start applying to premium job listings</li>
            </ul>

            <p>Need help? Our premium support team is available 24/7 to assist you.</p>
            
            <p>Best wishes for your job search!</p>
            <p>The JobConnect Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="{{linkedinUrl}}">LinkedIn</a> |
                <a href="{{twitterUrl}}">Twitter</a> |
                <a href="{{facebookUrl}}">Facebook</a>
            </div>
            <p>You received this email because you subscribed to JobConnect</p>
            <p>Email sent to: {{userEmail}}</p>
            <p>Â© {{currentYear}} JobConnect. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>Ahemdabad</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>